OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads for failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,FAdverts for nutrition brands Zoe and
OL,7,FHuel featuring Dragons' Den star
OL,8,FSteven Bartlett have been banned for
OL,9,Ffailing to disclose their commercial
OL,10,Frelationship with the celebrity
OL,11,Fentrepreneur.
OL,13,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,14,F(ASA) found the ads, seen on Facebook
OL,15,Fin February, "omitted material
OL,16,Finformation" about their links to
OL,17,FBartlett, who published the best-
OL,18,Fselling book The Diary Of A CEO ` 33
OL,19,FLaws For Business And Life and hosted
OL,20,Fthe podcast The Diary Of A CEO.
