OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads for failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,FBartlett is an investor in Zoe and a
OL,7,Fdirector at Huel.
OL,9,FThe ASA found the two adverts for Huel
OL,10,Fand one for Zoe were misleading or
OL,11,Flikely to mislead consumers.
OL,13,FThe advert for Zoe, which offers
OL,14,Fhealth testing and dietary advice
OL,15,Fservices, featured an image of
OL,16,FBartlett with a Zoe patch on his arm,
OL,17,Fwith text in the form of a quote from
OL,18,FBartlett which stated: "If you haven't
OL,19,Ftried Zoe yet, give it a shot. It
OL,20,Fmight just change your life."
