OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads for failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,FDefending the ad, Zoe said the average
OL,7,Fconsumer would understand that there
OL,8,Fwas a commercial relationship if a
OL,9,Fcelebrity appeared in an ad for a
OL,10,Fbrand, and argued that the consumer
OL,11,Fdid not need to know the exact nature
OL,12,Fof that relationship.
OL,14,FZoe said that if it was obliged to
OL,15,Finclude a specific disclosure about
OL,16,Fthe nature of Bartlett's status as an
OL,17,Finvestor in Zoe, this would have a
OL,18,Fwider impact on other brands and
OL,19,Finfluencers.
