OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads for failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,FHuel, known for its vitamin-enriched
OL,7,Ffood items ` whose ads featured
OL,8,FBartlett stating that its Daily Greens
OL,9,Fpowder was the "best product" it had
OL,10,Freleased, argued that consumers had no
OL,11,Fdoubt about the existence of such
OL,12,Fcommercial relationships when they saw
OL,13,Fthe endorsement within a paid-for ad
OL,14,Ftaken out by a company.
OL,16,FThis expectation removed the need for
OL,17,Fthe commercial relationship to be
OL,18,Fexplicitly stated, Huel claimed.
